webpackJsonp([0x61c7d5055313],{1886:function(A,e){A.exports={data:{markdownRemark:{html:'<p><strong>Snail mucus</strong> caught the attention of many skincare companies in Korea as this odd ingredient is famous for its skin-repairing and anti-aging properties, particularly useful in healing the skin post-breakout, and a good humectant.</p>\n<p>Since I really fond of anti-aging skincare product and haven\'t used any snail creams yet, I decided to buy a set of <strong>The Skin House Wrinkle Snail System Cream 100ml</strong> and <strong>Real Snail Wrinkle Free eye cream</strong>, with only 18,400krw (50% discount on <a href="https://www.memebox.com/" target="_blank">memebox.com</a>). In this post, I will review the snail cream only. I will review the eye cream later in the next post.</p>\n<h2 id="package"><a href="#package" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor"><svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>Package</h2>\n<p>The cream comes in a plastic dark brown jar with a golden lid that\'s as clear as a mirror. No spatula.</p>\n<figure style="width: 550px" class="align-center">\n  \n  <a class="gatsby-resp-image-link" href="/static/snail-1-5a62f6ecac90d44d1ef31d67aee10d89-5be7c.png" style="display: block" target="_blank" rel="noopener">\n  \n  <span class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper" style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 1020px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">\n    <span class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image" style="padding-bottom: 84.60784313725489%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;">\n      <img class="gatsby-resp-image-image" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;" alt="snail 1" title="" src="/static/snail-1-5a62f6ecac90d44d1ef31d67aee10d89-5be7c.png" srcset="/static/snail-1-5a62f6ecac90d44d1ef31d67aee10d89-5a8cd.png 300w,\n/static/snail-1-5a62f6ecac90d44d1ef31d67aee10d89-5662a.png 600w,\n/static/snail-1-5a62f6ecac90d44d1ef31d67aee10d89-5be7c.png 1020w" sizes="(max-width: 1020px) 100vw, 1020px">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<h2 id="texture"><a href="#texture" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor"><svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>Texture</h2>\n<p>The white cream is so thick and sticky, which makes it very difficult to take out (maybe all snail creams are sticky???). But once applying to skin, it goes smoothly.</p>\n<figure style="width: 550px" class="align-center">\n  \n  <a class="gatsby-resp-image-link" href="/static/snail-2-92d35e12dd34c4fdcfb88abbddfca96f-b7e98.png" style="display: block" target="_blank" rel="noopener">\n  \n  <span class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper" style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 906px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">\n    <span class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image" style="padding-bottom: 91.83222958057395%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;">\n      <img class="gatsby-resp-image-image" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;" alt="snail 2" title="" src="/static/snail-2-92d35e12dd34c4fdcfb88abbddfca96f-b7e98.png" srcset="/static/snail-2-92d35e12dd34c4fdcfb88abbddfca96f-6371f.png 300w,\n/static/snail-2-92d35e12dd34c4fdcfb88abbddfca96f-38b68.png 600w,\n/static/snail-2-92d35e12dd34c4fdcfb88abbddfca96f-b7e98.png 906w" sizes="(max-width: 906px) 100vw, 906px">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<h2 id="scent"><a href="#scent" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor"><svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>Scent</h2>\n<p>I have to say that the scent is the most uncomfortable thing about this cream. It smells like chemical to me.</p>\n<h2 id="ingredients"><a href="#ingredients" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor"><svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>Ingredients</h2>\n<p>You can check the ingredients in English <a href="http://www.cosdna.com/eng/cosmetic_e0f3320254.html" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>\n<h2 id="the-skin-house-says"><a href="#the-skin-house-says" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor"><svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>The Skin House says</h2>\n<p>This cream...</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Make your skin elastic and finely tight.</li>\n<li>Contain Adenosine and Snail Secretion Filtrate that manage the regenerative capacity of skin which gets worse gradually by aging.</li>\n<li>It is certified for its anti-wrinkle function from the Korea Food and Drug Administration, and All Kills the skin which is deprived of elasticity.</li>\n<li>Make the wrinkled and drooped skin to be tight and elastic, and is a trouble-solving broker for complex skin troubles.</li>\n<li>Make the dry and loose skin to be moist and glossy for 24 hours.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id="how-to-use"><a href="#how-to-use" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor"><svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>How to use</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>As a finishing cream: Before going to bed, at the last step of the basic skin care, apply an adequate amount and tap it lightly to be absorbed.</li>\n<li>As a massage gel for sensitive skin: When your skin becomes sensitive by the external stimulus, use toner to smooth the skin texture and apply the snail cream thickly, then massage it softly. </li>\n<li>As a moisturizing &#x26; nourishing pack: Use toner to smooth the skin texture and apply the snail cream thickly, leave it for 15~20 minutes, and then rinse off.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This cream is used as the last step in my skincare routine. Just use a little amount is enough.</p>\n<figure style="width: 650px" class="align-center">\n  \n  <a class="gatsby-resp-image-link" href="/static/snail-3-063c1601ad3a2c92b980700134772a91-615a1.png" style="display: block" target="_blank" rel="noopener">\n  \n  <span class="gatsby-resp-image-wrapper" style="position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 1200px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">\n    <span class="gatsby-resp-image-background-image" style="padding-bottom: 34.946236559139784%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;">\n      <img class="gatsby-resp-image-image" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;" alt="snail 3" title="" src="/static/snail-3-063c1601ad3a2c92b980700134772a91-abe1c.png" srcset="/static/snail-3-063c1601ad3a2c92b980700134772a91-10046.png 300w,\n/static/snail-3-063c1601ad3a2c92b980700134772a91-3c4a3.png 600w,\n/static/snail-3-063c1601ad3a2c92b980700134772a91-abe1c.png 1200w,\n/static/snail-3-063c1601ad3a2c92b980700134772a91-615a1.png 1674w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px">\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n  <figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<h2 id="i-say"><a href="#i-say" aria-hidden="true" class="anchor"><svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"></path></svg></a>I say</h2>\n<p>To be honest, I don’t really see fancy effects on my skin as advertising. This cream is so thick and sticky that I only use it before bedtime. It does help improve my skin elasticity and remove some minimal wrinkle, but just a little. My face feels heavy and sticky whenever I use. It also takes quite long to fully absorb but the stickiness is still though it doesn’t make my face glossy. Even so, my skin still feels dry as it’s not well- moisturized. Overall, this cream is so heavy and sticky with an uncomfortable scent that is too much for summer but not enough moisture for winter. I stop using it on my face now and just use it as a hand cream instead.</p>',timeToRead:3,excerpt:"Snail mucus  caught the attention of many skincare companies in Korea as this odd ingredient is famous for its skin-repairing and anti-aging…",frontmatter:{title:"Review - The Skin House Wrinkle Snail System Cream",cover:"/images/snail.png",date:"2017/07/04",category:"Beauty",tags:["Beauty","wrinkle-snail-system-cream","snail-cream","skin-care","moisturizer","kemocsen","skin-house","kem-oc-sen","duong-da"]},fields:{slug:"/en/Review-The-Skin-House-Wrinkle-Snail-System-Cream/"}}},pathContext:{path:"/en/Review-The-Skin-House-Wrinkle-Snail-System-Cream/",langKey:"en"}}}});
//# sourceMappingURL=path---en-review-the-skin-house-wrinkle-snail-system-cream-624cffd8ce0080aa1de4.js.map